==English==
===Etymology===
From the Swahili phrase '''hakuna matata,''' popularized in the [[West]] by the [[w:Walt Disney|Disney]] [[production]], ''[[w:The Lion King|The Lion King.]]''
===Idiom===
'''hakuna matata'''
# [[take it easy|Take it easy.]]
'''Usage note:''' It is not used in [[conversation]].